3. Introduction to JSX
---------------------------------------------------------------
###################################################
Imagine you have a magic notebook where you can write both stories and instructions for your toys. JSX is like that magic notebook, but for building websites! It lets you mix HTML (which looks like a story) with JavaScript (which is like instructions) in one place.

------------------
Why Use JSX?
------------------

i. Easier to Read: Just like how it's easier to read a story with pictures, JSX makes it easier to understand what your website will look like.

ii. More Powerful: You can write instructions (JavaScript) right inside your story (HTML), making your website smart and interactive.

iii. Simpler: Instead of writing separate instructions and stories, you can keep everything together, making it simpler to build and manage.

